						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">dougeff wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">But, I haven't seen any code that does this sort of thing for 6502...am I thinking about this issue correctly?</div><br />Yeah, by rounding to nearest you can minimize the amount of error, but you have to consider whether it's worth the performance hit. I'm sure many games/apps on 6502 round down without thinking twice about it.</div>

					
